title: [A Nalfein's Favor]
[Jiarine's Outfitting]
[Jiarine's General Store]
description: Grey watered silk walls rise from a glossy black ebonwood floor.  Just above some puffed raw silk pillows hangs a painted silk wall panel, and a low skylight-set ceiling completes the picture.  Some carved haon pegs and a iron-bound ebonwood chest stand side by side in the middle of the room.
